item.description:
I have included "quickemu" which helps to download and boot virtual machines.
Unfortunately at boot time it gives me some errors, but the images it
downloads work if I start qemu in the usual ways I normally use.
So I'm leaving it because even just for that it is very useful.
The errors it gives are on spice and in creating the pid file.
I try to start at the command line with the script created by the same program,
the images go to segfault. If you have any suggestions they are welcome.
Please forgive my bad English.
